Amy Jo Johnson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amy_Jo_Johnson 0 Amy Jo Johnson (born October 6, 1970) is an American Canadian actress, filmmaker, singer-songwriter, and director. Johnson began her acting career in her early twenties, in Mighty Morphin Power Rangers, and, after she left the series, went onto star in Felicity, The Division, and Flashpoint while pursuing a career as a musician and a filmmaker.
